#: ../../source/installation.rst:18
msgid "安装在 **全局** 的好处是所有项目都可以调用同一套库，可以直接调用命令而不需要先切换环境和目录；"
msgstr ""
"Installing **globally** allows all projects to use the same library, and "
"commands can be called directly without switching environments and "
